(9... exd4 10. Bg2 Qe6 11. Bxc6+ bxc6 12. f3 $17) 10. Bg2 $15 Qd6 (10... Qd7
$142 11. Rb1 a6 $15) 11. f4 $2 (11. Rb1 a6 $11) 11... Bxe2 $4 {throwing away
